nd more than $1.55 million has been donated to 79 projects across 34 countries. \u003c/p\u003e\n \u003cp\u003eThis year’s edition, which features 20 winners from the \u003ca href=\"https://rememberingwildlife.awardsplatform.com/page/zkEyvjko\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003eassociated photo contest\u003c/a\u003e, received an impressive 4,500 submitted photos. The winning photographs, all featured below, come from photographers all around the world, including in the United States, Brazil, Kenya, Namibia, Australia, and more. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_791554\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-791554\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/DSF3885_couleurs-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A lioness stands alert on a rocky, sandy shore with ocean waves crashing in the background under a cloudy sky.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/DSF3885_couleurs-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/DSF3885_couleurs-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/DSF3885_couleurs-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/DSF3885_couleurs-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/DSF3885_couleurs-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/DSF3885_couleurs-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/DSF3885_couleurs.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-791554\"\u003eGriet Van Malderen (Switzerland): Lioness, Namibia\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_791553\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-791553\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/L7A5352-800x522.jpg\" alt=\"A black and white photo of an adult elephant and a baby elephant standing in shallow water. The baby reaches its trunk up toward the adult, and they appear to be interacting affectionately.\" width=\"800\" height=\"522\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/L7A5352-800x522.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/L7A5352-320x209.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/L7A5352-1536x1002.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/L7A5352.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-791553\"\u003eJagdeep Rajput (India): Elephant, Corbett National Park, India\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_791551\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-791551\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/2024-Kenya-183A4270-2-800x513.jpg\" alt=\"Two rhinos clash head-to-head, their horns locked and mud flying around them, capturing the intensity of their fight in a close-up wildlife scene.\" width=\"800\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/2024-Kenya-183A4270-2-800x513.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/2024-Kenya-183A4270-2-320x205.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/2024-Kenya-183A4270-2-1536x984.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/2024-Kenya-183A4270-2.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-791551\"\u003eAlessandro Marena (Italy): Rhino, Solio Game Reserve, Laikipia, Kenya\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_791550\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-791550\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Age-of-Innocence-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A polar bear lies on snow while three playful cubs climb on and around her, with soft sunlight creating a warm, serene atmosphere in the snowy landscape.\" width=\"800