etapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/babygorillas-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Two young gorillas playfully hang from tree branches in a lush, green forest. Both gorillas have open mouths, appearing to smile or call out while surrounded by dense foliage.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/babygorillas-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/babygorillas-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/babygorillas-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/babygorillas-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/babygorillas-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/babygorillas-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/babygorillas.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-791548\"\u003ePedro Amaral (Portugal): Gorillas, Bwindi Impenetrable Forest, Uganda\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_791547\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-791547\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Bengal_Tiger_Reflection-567x800.jpg\" alt=\"A tiger lies on the ground, drinking water from a pond. Its face is reflected clearly in the water, surrounded by dry leaves and natural forest floor.\" width=\"567\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Bengal_Tiger_Reflection-567x800.jpg 567w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Bengal_Tiger_Reflection-227x320.jpg 227w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Bengal_Tiger_Reflection-1088x1536.jpg 1088w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Bengal_Tiger_Reflection.jpg 1133w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 567px) 100vw, 567px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-791547\"\u003eBircan Harper (UK): Tiger, Bandhavgarh National Park, India\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003